context_bundle.summary: Web dashboard for Carbyne. localhost:7778, real-time WebSocket updates, shows agent status, message flow, tool calls, tasks, alerts. Browser-based, low build cost.

onboarding.quick_start: Web-based Carbyne dashboard. HTTP server on 7778, WebSocket for live updates. Shows: agent status, message flow, tool calls, task queue, alerts. React or vanilla JS frontend. Carbyne serves static files + WS endpoint.
common_patterns: HTTP on localhost:7778 serving static HTML/JS
Panels: agents, messages, tools, tasks, alerts
Pulls from Carbyne state.json + live events
